org.rsna.ctp.pipeline

Class Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rsna.ctp.pipeline.Status

  • public class Status
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to encapsulate typesafe enum return status values for CTP services. This class provides static final instances for each of the possible operational results (OK, FAIL, RETRY).

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static Status FAIL
      Status value indicating that an operation failed and retrying will also fail.
      static Status OK
      Status value indicating that an operation completed successfully.
      static Status RETRY
      Status value indicating that an operation failed but retrying may succeed.
